{"tid":1714400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"股市仲可以如期開市，大家點睇？","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:23:21.000Z","uid":46947,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e87f7d370130afd9a415bcd7364f06ea07ae16c1","tid":1714400,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c0559ce04d2615ab9cd7b7204d1ab61fd65afb","tid":1714400,"uid":18912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"預左"},{"pid":"33987c34fa16f769b3367b0c2a7c58cddc280f76","tid":1714400,"uid":278228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:05:35.000Z","msg":"借po一個位<br />\n大家好，示威其實都4個月<br />\n我地每次行動都會影響到民生，<br />\n琴日我係沙田去暴大，<br />\n沿途好多街彷屌road block，又話過分乜乜77<br />\n但冇人提過黑警好似殺人咁攻中大<br />\n因為呢件事<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔關佢事</span></strong></span><br />\n每次咁辛苦做咁多野，到頭嚟都係要比人屌<br />\n既然係咁，<br />\n大家係咪時候諗下要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直搗皇龍</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔關政見問題，係有的確為所不少既人只關注生計<br />\n同有冇屋企番，甚至會主動清road block<br />\n即使唔係撐警<br />\n既然守中大又要送頭，守旺角又要通頂<br />\n但係都迫唔到政府做啲乜<br />\n<br />\n4個月喇<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解宜家仲唔升級去搞啲官</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n至少仲會多人支持<br />\n<br />\n策略：小隊突擊，人在明我在暗<br />\n<br />\n要救中大就要有大啲話語權，宜家有話語權既係官"},{"pid":"f0812c43c74f2a477567503e665dba9e33c4e2fc","tid":1714400,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:05:59.000Z","msg":"11.14 曙光行動 繼續三罷<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/evpMOT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/evpMOT</a>"},{"pid":"8ab7744d51c3b11e98e734b9d8768cd3b5100552","tid":1714400,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-1